    "description": "Exostation is a sci-fi real-time strategy game. Reach sustainable planet economies by building, allocating, mining, and selling wisely. Allow humanity to spread and conquer new solar systems not by war but by ensuring its planet's resources are not exhausted.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d4fdb6431e3b9a7d81462e6ce1323d18.poster.avif?t=1674494102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d4fdb6431e3b9a7d81462e6ce1323d18.webm?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d4fdb6431e3b9a7d81462e6ce1323d18.mp4?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help humanity become a multi-planetary species</h2><br>Earth is not the only planet humanity can live on anymore. A multi-planetary species means new planets to discover and develop.<br>As a space explorer, you will explore new solar systems, it will be your responsibility to build each planet's economy. Sustainability is the key!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/74074f8dfd3ebde6460edf5edd196ef6.poster.avif?t=1674494102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/74074f8dfd3ebde6460edf5edd196ef6.webm?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/74074f8dfd3ebde6460edf5edd196ef6.mp4?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Exostations on new worlds</h2><br>Before growing the population of a new planet, fulfilling their basic needs is required. You will have to ensure there is enough food and water to feed them and enough shelter for them to survive. Build farms, water pumps, and housing.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d2018d0e48ca49ddc87b69ae07422a9d.poster.avif?t=1674494102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d2018d0e48ca49ddc87b69ae07422a9d.webm?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/d2018d0e48ca49ddc87b69ae07422a9d.mp4?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Trade goods with other planets to develop further</h2><br>To become sustainable, exchanging goods with other planets is necessary. Extract <strong>metals</strong> by building <strong>mines</strong>, transform them into <strong>goods</strong> in your <strong>factories</strong> and <strong>sell</strong> those via your <strong>market</strong>. You will then obtain more money to develop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/ecaa98be7b6e4837e034f3c8109c869f.poster.avif?t=1674494102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/ecaa98be7b6e4837e034f3c8109c869f.webm?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/ecaa98be7b6e4837e034f3c8109c869f.mp4?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be mindful of your actions</h2><br>Choose where you will build your next farm or mine carefully, and leverage the placement bonuses to get the best results.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/a646f106793f403e3afaa6c6b1613eec.poster.avif?t=1674494102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/a646f106793f403e3afaa6c6b1613eec.webm?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2278840/extras/a646f106793f403e3afaa6c6b1613eec.mp4?t=1674494102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
